data.description: Parade of Homes winner, semi custom all brick home on a 1/2 acre lot! This 4 bed 2 bath home is stunning with an open floor plan where the kitchen overlooks the family room. Custom features include 9 foot ceilings, recessed lighting, upgraded ceiling fans and light fixtures just name a few! Gourmet kitchen features Craftsman's modern square cabinets, full extension drawer guides with dovetail joints and soft close. Backsplash and shelving add to the clean look. Large pantry with upgraded shelving. Island and beautiful counter tops. Stainless steel appliances complete the modern yet comfortable kitchen. Ceiling fans in all the bedrooms and recessed lighting. Primary suite has barn door leading to the bath. Separate his and hers vanities! Linen closet and water closet for privacy. Fully tiled shower, shampoo niche and frameless glass door complete this beautiful ensuite bath. Large walk in closet with laundry area just off primary bedroom for convenience. Guest bath with oversized 6 drawer vanity for lots of storage. Blinds included throughout home. French doors lead to huge extended back patio with covered area. Fully fenced with a double gate yard. A half acre lot too. Irrigation system. This home is immaculate, better than new, and move in ready!
